snippet.title: Star Trek Online: Awakening - Official Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/star-trek-online-ps4/

Awakening is now available on PlayStation®4!

Captains, it's time to return to 2410! With our newest content update, Anthony Rapp joins the cast of Star Trek Online - reprising his role as Commander Paul Stamets from Star Trek: Discovery. Enter the Mycelial network to put a stop to the Klingon's dastardly plan to damage the fabric of the entire universe.
